title: Atomix Virtual DJ Pro V5.0.7
description:
Atomix Virtual DJ Pro V5.0.7 :Atomix Virtual DJ Program for mixing MP3 in the real time, with the aid of it you will be able to make outstanding miks. Program is suitable both for the novices and for those moved DJ. also Atomix Virtual DJ contains many effects and washes for DJ. it includes such possibilities as: the automatic \"trimming\" of the speed of tracks, the indication of a change in the loudness level in the track, the splendid imitation of vinyl plates, auto-information of tracks, the possibility to memorize to 9 positions in the track, many plaginov for treating the sound, the 3rd strip equalizer, the possibility of the record of miksa in wav and mp3 and much other...
